</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_264" id="131v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_264_r1l1">Göcʒen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Aſchuſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l2">Amptman cʒü krawtheim / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_264_r1l3">Lieber Göcʒ / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Chüncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Swarcʒe<ex>n</ex>berg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Dietrichs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / Darvmb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l5">den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒe rede geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / Die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l6">güte die er <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / da hab er recht cʒü vnd leıpgeding daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l7">des er auch güte vrkünd hab / . vnd beger nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l8">mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auſcʒetragen / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd </del> Wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l9">vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_264" id="131v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Göczen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Aschusen, amptman czü Krawtheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Göcz, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Chüncze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Swarcze<ex>n</ex>berg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und Dietrichs
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, darumb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> cze rede gesaczt und
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,
                        die güte, die er <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, da hab er recht czü
                        und leipgeding daran, des er auch güte urkünd hab. Und beger nicht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das mit
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ausczetragen. Wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und
                            <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.</ab>
</div>
